overview: "My favorite scene is the first, with Omar dominating Laura Picasso, the Swiss girl. Completely real and submissive. Laura had written me a letter saying she wanted to work with me, (like Sandy did in the earlier days for 'Sandy Insatiable'). She is a normal girl and wanted to have an experience making a movie with me. Laura is open for the worst that the human mind can imagine. Omar also did great domination over the French girl Cecilia Vega. Cecilia is an unbelievable actress and she was very good sexually." - Rocco
title: Rocco: Puppet Master 2
